      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so the-- a chauffeur came and drove us to s'-Hertogenbosch, to Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Van Mackelenbergh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my brother and I, we cried, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, this is only going to be a little while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm going to visit you in the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that made us feel better.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then from there, we went to camp Vught, which is very close to s'-Hertogenbosch.",
